{"tid":307340,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"小賓周睇假波講故台（一）(巴車黑哨大戰)","createTime":"2017-07-03T09:41:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T09:58:53.000Z","uid":126314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"65ba4fccc21213a1c9454e874bb76d17f30a6dce","tid":307340,"uid":126314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T09:41:31.000Z","msg":"一世人流流長 總會睇到幾場經典假波 唔知有幾多清一齊睇過<br />\n<br />\n而當年十幾歲 睇完依場波就學識曬所有粗口 (中，英版) 究竟有幾[black]黑[/black] <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fvFKn1VRw1g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfvFKn1VRw1g&d=vETYuIEwvbn%2BH6dyMCsmrMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=ea19c018\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fvFKn1VRw1g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">碧基用手拍波 </span>(無十二碼)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">艾比度手推腳踢巴哥</span>(無套餐) （依下我係屌到想打爆部電視）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">伊度奧</span>舉高隻手擋射門 （無十二碼）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">艾維斯禁區外拉到入禁區內</span> （ 無十二碼)<br />\n<br />\n到底依場波點先有十二碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  真係唔知<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/toTx8wet820\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtoTx8wet820&d=vETYuIEwvbn%2BH6dyMCsmrMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=0e9a5dfb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/toTx8wet820</a><br />\n<br />\n我姐係想講句(<span style=\"color: red;\">屌您啦巴狗</span> 唔知以為依場係欖球  唔係有依場 [black]您地會開始到夢三[/black]？"},{"pid":"364579141e531e6bfb8130d8f5e244cedee8efe2","tid":307340,"uid":91152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T09:43:54.000Z","msg":"呢場波應該三十年後仲會講"},{"pid":"78c3ade0ffbb9218b50e87c361a50d56f8ff0ef8","tid":307340,"uid":126314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T09:57:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢場波應該三十年後仲會講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真心依場波點講都有得講落去"},{"pid":"fc044541397a99e61739a3ea60b0b86e183bc9a8","tid":307340,"uid":91875,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T09:58:53.000Z","msg":"其實獌係費蛇年代果堆都有排清算"}]}